metadata.name: PLATIN BY JOKER´S CHERRYS
metadata.description:
Here a small presentation of Joker´s Cherrys NFT.

Learn more about the project on the Joker's Cherrys website.


Allocation: 1777 NFTs total.

1000 Gold for 0.069 $ETH: Claim 1 bottle of finest Joker's Cherrys Sour Cherry Liquer just for the shipping cost, access raffles, access to JC Discord, Airdrops, Discounts at Joker´s Cherrys Shopify Store, free access to JC drinking game app (after completion).

700 Platin for 0.169 $ETH: All benefits from Silver + invitation to certain JC events, voting right for future decisions!

77 Black for 0.3 $ETH: All benefits from Gold & Platin + JC surprise Box, free access to all JC events, preferential sale VIP Tickets for all future JC events.

Over time, all levels will receive more utilitys, be curious.

100 Gold, 70 Platin and 22 Black NFTs are retained for future team members and cooperations.

Life is a Joke!
